  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "...",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Which part of United States are you from?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:00:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Illinois.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:00:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh Illinois! And how long have you been living in France?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:00:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Uh, four months.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:00:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How did you get so lucky to move to Paris?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:00:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hmm, I wanted to improve my French.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:00:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I work here now. I have a job with a French marketing firm.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:00:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I work for a big marketing firm in Chicago,",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:00:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "but I acquired a smaller marketing firm here.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:00:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm kind of like the American point of view.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, so you're studying French now?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:00:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah, I've been studying at my office.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:00:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Uh-huh.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Did you study French in US?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:00:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I did. Yeah.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:00:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Two years at high school and three years at university.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:01:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So you're pretty good at French now.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:01:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, I wouldn't say that.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:01:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "My spoken French isn't that great.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:01:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm better at reading and writing than I am at speaking.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:01:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Really?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:01:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:01:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So, how's the Paris office treating you?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:01:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "They're a fun bunch.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:01:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Did you experience any culture shock when you arrived?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:01:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Uh, yeah. Some.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:01:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "In what way?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:01:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Manor is very incredibly important for the French people.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:01:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This was one of the biggest culture shock examples in France for me.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:01:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "There's always a merci or silvoublier,",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:01:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "tacked on to any interaction at a store.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:01:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And people are addressed as madame or messieurs.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:01:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's cute.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:01:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What do you like about living in France?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:01:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The food is so delicious.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:01:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm obsessed with French cheeses and croissants,",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:01:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "which are buttery, crispy and delicious for breakfast.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:02:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The fashion is so chic.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:02:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The lights are so magical.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:02:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What do you find difficult about living in France?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:02:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The language.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:02:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Even though I studied French for five years,",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:02:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I find it really hard to communicate.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:02:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I think in general,",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:02:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "French people expect the visitors to speak really good French.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:02:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And they look annoyed if you get something wrong.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:02:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What impressed you the most so far?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:02:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Everything is impressive in Paris.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:02:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The small cheese shops, the meat shops,",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:02:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "the get stores, wine shops,",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:02:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "people sitting on sidewalk cafes.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:02:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Have you been to Louvre Museum?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:02:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I have.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:02:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It was excellent.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:02:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Fantastic.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:02:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you miss your home?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:03:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Of course, I love France and feel grateful to have the opportunity to live here.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:03:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But at the end of the day, there's no place like home.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:03:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Does it always rain so much here?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:03:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes, it usually does.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:03:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We're on the throne.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:03:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's rarely storms.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:03:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It doesn't often storm here, but it rains frequently.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:03:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's good.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:03:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I don't like storms because they usually scare me.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:03:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's the lightning and thunder that bother me.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:03:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And the strong winds.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:03:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's what does the damage in a storm.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:03:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I can't extremely nervous.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:03:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm never scared of storms.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:03:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, what are you afraid of?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:03:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I am scared of spiders.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:03:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And how long have you had this bobaia?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:03:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I've had it since I was about seven.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:03:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Did something happen to start the bobaia?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:03:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I remember a very big spider in the apartment that we lived in at the time.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:03:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Coming out from under the television, I'm going across the room.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:04:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And me being absolutely terrified.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:04:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And that's the first time I remember being scared.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:04:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How does he defect to your life?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:04:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "In the past, it was really awful.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:04:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I mean, I couldn't sit in the same room as a spider.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:04:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And I always had to keep all the doors and windows shut.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:04:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Because I was frightened that spiders might come in.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:04:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But now I can sit in the same room as a spider,",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:04:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "and I can put it in the glass and take it outside myself if I have to.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:04:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "If there's nobody else there.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:04:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So, it doesn't affect me as badly as it did before,",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:04:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "but I still don't like them.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:04:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Would other things are your afraid of?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:04:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Uh, let me think.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:04:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How about clowns?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:04:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No, clowns do not usually scare me.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:04:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What about big dogs?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:04:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes, big dogs always scare me.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:05:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I always get afraid whenever one of them gets too near me.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:05:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That makes to of us.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:05:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You don't look so well lately, Dan.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:05:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Are you okay?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:05:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, I've been feeling out of sore sleep lately.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:05:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I've not been sleeping well at all, and I can't concentrate.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:05:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Maybe I should see a doctor.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:05:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You need to take care of yourself.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:05:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You need to make your body strong.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:05:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How can I possibly do that?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:05:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's not that hard.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:05:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "First, you should eat healthy food.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:05:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I eat only healthy food, but I still don't feel good.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:05:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh yeah? What do you eat?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:05:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "In the morning, I eat frozen waffles, muffins, and flavored yogurt.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:05:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Then, at noon, I eat a hamburger or a pizza.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:05:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "For dinner, I will always have salty french fries with lots of ketchup.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:06:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "ketchup is very healthy, you know.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:06:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It comes from tomatoes.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:06:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "For dessert, I eat ice cream, which contains milk, so it's very healthy too.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:06:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That doesn't sound very healthy to me.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:06:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Maybe you should improve your diet.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:06:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, how should I do that?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:06:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "First of all, maybe you can add in a big salad once a day.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:06:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You know, a big salad with lots of fresh vegetables.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:06:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay, I can do that, I guess.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:06:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I can have a big salad with lots of fresh vegetables once a day.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:06:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I know you have a job that requires you to sit all day.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:06:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you ever work out?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:06:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Unfortunately, I never find time to fit that goal into my schedule.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:06:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So I have a pretty sedentary lifestyle.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:06:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You don't need a gym membership or an exercise machine in your basement to stay active.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:07:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Instead of cramming into your offices crowded elevator every morning, you can take the stairs.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:07:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Use this as an opportunity to get some exercise.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:07:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Park your car further away from your workplace or home to seize the chance to sneak in in extra few steps.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:07:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Thanks for the tips.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:07:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm sure there'll be very helpful.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:07:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Are you a morning person, Susan?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:07:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes, I am. On weekdays, I get a very early at 545.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:07:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Why?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:07:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you have to be at work so early?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:07:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No, I start work nine.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:07:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So why do you wake up so early then?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:07:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "First of all, early morning is quiet.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:07:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Nobody phones me at 6am.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:07:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "There aren't any important emails or messages to answer.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:08:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "There aren't any meetings. There aren't any people.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:08:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The morning is my time.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:08:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I prefer to do things in the morning when I have energy.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:08:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I do exercise for 30 minutes in my home gym and have a big breakfast.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:08:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Then I get ready for work and drive to the office.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:08:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "When I get to the building where I work, I go for a walk around a local park.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:08:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Then I go inside the start work at 9 o'clock.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:08:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And on Thursdays, I get up even earlier at 520am to study German.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:08:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Getting up early helps me do more during the day.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:08:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm usually tired in the evening after a day at work.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:08:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And when I'm tired, the last thing I want to do is to exercise.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:08:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sort of study or to practice a musical instrument.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:08:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I find it impossible to get up early.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:09:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How can you do it?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:09:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You can start by setting your alarm five minutes earlier than you usually get up.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:09:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And the next day, set it five minutes earlier again.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:09:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "After three weeks, you'll have nearly two hours that you never had before.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:09:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Getting up early is a big help if you have a lot of things to do.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:09:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's better to go to bed early and have shorter evenings and longer mornings.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:09:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I don't think I want to change my schedule and my lifestyle.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:09:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I love to go to bed late and spending time watching TV, seeing my friends, and spending time on social media.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:09:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you ever tell lies, Trisha?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:09:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I do sometimes, but only little white lies.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:09:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You know, like telling my sister who knew hair style is great.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:09:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "When I really don't like it, stuff like that.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:10:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh yeah, I also told my mom that I loved the gift she got me from my birthday.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:10:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Even though I actually really hated it.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:10:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So you've never told any bad lies?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:10:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, to tell you the truth, I did tell a bad lie last year.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:10:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I wanted to borrow my friend Judy's blouse to wear it at my school dance,",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:10:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "but she refused to lend it to me.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:10:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Really? Yes, but I didn't want to give up.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:10:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So I lied to her that I was sick, and that I might have to go into the hospital the following week.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:10:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So I didn't know when I'd be able to go to a dance again.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:10:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "She felt sorry for me and decided to lend me her blouse.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:10:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That was a bad lie indeed.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:10:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're right. Then, as if that wasn't bad enough, there's more.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:10:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I was dancing with my friends when someone bumped into me and spilled a dream all over my blouse.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:11:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm so sorry.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:11:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It was strawberry juice, and the blouse was white.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:11:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, what a bad luck.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:11:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I guess the blouse was ruined, right?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:11:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Exactly.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:11:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And not only the blouse was ruined, but our friendship too.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:11:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Because Judy found out that my story about the hospital was just a lie.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:11:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "She just wouldn't let it slide.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:11:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's too bad.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:11:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Maybe she would forgive you one day and trust you again.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:11:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I sure they hoped so.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:11:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I learned my lesson though.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:11:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I would never lie to a friend like that ever again.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:11:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Did you like school, Anthony?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:11:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I didn't hate school, but I don't think I liked it very much.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:11:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I used to enjoy PE. I quite liked English and Spanish, but there were lots of subjects I didn't like.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:11:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I didn't like math very much.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:12:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "History was boring, and I found science difficult.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:12:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I had a small group of friends and used to spend time with them talking about sport, talking about music.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:12:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So it wasn't too bad, but I didn't like it very much.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:12:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What about you?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:12:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Did you like school?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:12:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah, most of the time.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:12:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I always really looked forward to getting back to school.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:12:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What did you like about it?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:12:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, I had some good friends, and I liked learning things.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:12:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But there were some subjects that I didn't like very much, and I hated PE.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:12:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I used to invent a lot of excuses, like saying that I was ill, because I didn't want to do it.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:12:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Elementary school was all fun, and we had great teachers.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:12:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "High school was harder work, and we used to have lots of exams and tests.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:12:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But we had really inspiring teachers.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:13:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "My favorites were in math and biology.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:13:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And overall, yeah, I really liked it.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:13:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Did you have a favorite or least favorite teacher at school?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:13:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes, I liked the Spanish teacher.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:13:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "She was my favorite teacher, because she was Spanish, and she taught us to speak with a very good Spanish accent.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:13:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Did she inspire you?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:13:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "She did, and I'm still learning Spanish, and I go to Spain pretty often.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:13:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What's your biggest regret about school?",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:13:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, I wish I'd been more involved in school clubs.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:13:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Our school had lots of clubs, where you could do things,",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:13:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "like dance, or learn to play an instrument, or play chess, things like that.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:13:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's a shame, because I would have learned some really useful skills, I'm sure.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:13:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Thanks for watching, and be sure to subscribe to our YouTube channel for more videos like this.",
      "zh": "",
      "ja": "",
      "time": "00:14:09"
    }
  ]
}